  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836680/extras/4f2609dbd7d3528a08d3c828e11e7787.poster.avif?t=1755786274\" width=480 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836680/extras/4f2609dbd7d3528a08d3c828e11e7787.webm?t=1755786274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836680/extras/4f2609dbd7d3528a08d3c828e11e7787.mp4?t=1755786274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slidetracked is a minimalist puzzle game where you draw coloured paths to make Red and Blue reach their goals without getting in the way of each other. It starts out as simple as it looks, but gets challenging as you dig deeper into the subtleties and consequences of the mechanics. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique simultaneous sliding movement mechanic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover and get challenged  on your understanding of Red and Blue's movement logic in 60 hand made levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skip levels when you get stuck thanks to branching level selection</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Minimalist graphics and smooth animations </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dark mode for relaxed late night puzzling</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836680/extras/0893a68bf37f9f2f612c6fe06324bd37.poster.avif?t=1755786274\" width=480 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836680/extras/0893a68bf37f9f2f612c6fe06324bd37.webm?t=1755786274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836680/extras/0893a68bf37f9f2f612c6fe06324bd37.mp4?t=1755786274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836680/extras/4f2609dbd7d3528a08d3c828e11e7787.poster.avif?t=1755786274\" width=480 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836680/extras/4f2609dbd7d3528a08d3c828e11e7787.webm?t=1755786274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836680/extras/4f2609dbd7d3528a08d3c828e11e7787.mp4?t=1755786274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slidetracked is a minimalist puzzle game where you draw coloured paths to make Red and Blue reach their goals without getting in the way of each other. It starts out as simple as it looks, but gets challenging as you dig deeper into the subtleties and consequences of the mechanics. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique simultaneous sliding movement mechanic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover and get challenged  on your understanding of Red and Blue's movement logic in 60 hand made levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skip levels when you get stuck thanks to branching level selection</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Minimalist graphics and smooth animations </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dark mode for relaxed late night puzzling</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836680/extras/0893a68bf37f9f2f612c6fe06324bd37.poster.avif?t=1755786274\" width=480 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836680/extras/0893a68bf37f9f2f612c6fe06324bd37.webm?t=1755786274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836680/extras/0893a68bf37f9f2f612c6fe06324bd37.mp4?t=1755786274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
